- file, subject, code, version, valid_from, practice_number, title, groups,
- analysisResult: {
    groups: integer,
    materials: {
      equipment:   [ { quantity_per_group:int, unit:string, description:string }, … ],
      supplies:    [ { quantity_per_group:int, unit:string, description:string }, … ],
      reactives:   [ { quantity_per_group:int, unit:string, description:string }, … ]
    },
    creditsUsed: integer
}
Do NOT include any other fields, maps, markdown or comments.
